guage features extracted on series of data and downstream tasks. 
We choose MSR-VTT and DiDemo as downstream tasks. Larger 
value indicates larger domain gap.

Table 1. 
From the last column, we find that the NMI score between 
HD-VILA sub and downstream data is much larger than oth-
ers, especially for MSR-VTT dataset. This indicates that 
direct training with subtitles may introduce inconsistency 
with downstream tasks.
